{
  "stem": "9777.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Got acquainted with some young baker boys around the corner in a bakery.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they used to give me a little bit of bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, we had it on coupons, the bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they used to give it to me, you know, like, through the back door, a few rolls or-- didn't have to stand in a long line and wait for it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Too much nourishment, you know, like, we didn't really have.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They gave you, like, 20 ounces of meat or something of that sort for the week.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So sometime we got and sometime we didn't, but the butcher was in the same building.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So very, very little food as buying went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Was hard to come by account of the air raids, that-- which one didn't help much neither.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was too many of us to get any kind of special acknowledgement or help from it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even I had an extra acquaintance there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My rabbi from Pecs, he became one of the three of the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He expired, poor thing, just-- luckily, maybe, should we say, that-- in the wartime he died.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A young man.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Zolta Wallenstein.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He became one of the-- the three rabbis from the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They did help people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But people were very busy trying to find lost sons, husbands, which one were taken away for forced labor to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this was the-- the biggest job what they were trying to achieve.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then there was people, you know, they have no jobs, no means.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're being dislocated account of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were-- they did feed the people to certain degree.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that's all what it was to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Really they couldn't do much.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
